Package: rslurm
Type: Package
Title: Submit R calculations to the SLURM cluster
Version: 0.1.2
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: parallel,
    stringr
Date: 2015-06-24
Authors@R: person('Philippe', 'Marchand', email = 'pmarchand@sesync.org', 
                role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: This package was developed to simplify the R interface to 
    SESYNC's SLURM cluster and automate the process of spreading a calculation
    in parallel over cluster nodes.
License: GPL-3
